msgctxt "v5.3-whats-new"
msgid ""
"• A stylish layout for posts."
"• The ability to filter posts by author for multi-author blogs."
"• The ability to restore posts/pages from the trash bin."
"• Pages grouped by date."
"• The ability to search posts and pages."
"\n"
"• We’ve refreshed the color scheme in your Stats screen and replaced the floating spinner with a progress bar."
"• You can now authorize WordPress.com 2FA login using the app. If you log in into WordPress.com on your browser, the app will prompt you via a push notification and you’ll be able to choose whether to authorize the login."
"• “My Sites” is now a single list, instead of two."
msgstr ""
